    <section>
      <title>Introduction</title>
      <para>MynPad is a <emphasis>structure based, stylable, link and cloud enabled</emphasis> notepad. It reads and writes its contents in Docbook 5 format and the rendering of the individual elements can be customized through a style sheet.</para>
    </section>

